        <date>1926</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still from the feature film ‘Datorie şi sacrificiu’ (Duty and sacrifice) shows a man and woman in front of a big wooden cross. The kneeling woman is praying. The man is looking down at her. In the distance, the shape of a house can be made out, as well as a group of houses even further away.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was directed by Ion Sahighian and released in 1926.</ab>
